				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-o1hzh7z elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="o1hzh7z" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p>In 2017 we launced<strong>  Global Recycle Group </strong> as a professional mobile phones and phone parts supplier. During the early stages, we get to know how most companies are really struggling to find a right mobile supplier to cater for their needs based on quality service, we felt the people&#8217;s needs were simple- high-quality parts, a reliable service, and reasonable prices. We, therefore, decided to establish in Hongkong for the needs and we quickly found the right response from all of the companies who started to work with us because the quality was extremely good and the service was second to none due to our vast years of experience.</p><p><strong>Gradually our passion for quality services was more established in several countries, with numerous supply across Europe and other countries</strong> we had handed a selected fantastic supply chain that we felt comfortable with to deliver a second to none service. In that time, we have outgrown our warehouse location once and recently doubled the size of our existing warehouse to cater for thousands of extra phones,parts and accessories.</p><p>At Global Recycle Group, we believe in good faith never compromise quality over price, which is definitely what we stand for and Global Recycle Group has found other competitors do in the previous years by using substandard parts In their reconditioned devices or mixing the used stock with reconditioned ones, we receive brutally honest instant feedback regularly regards that. Our technical skills about the industry is long enough to know it’s pros and cons to getting everything perfect all the time, but by having quick and reliable feedback it can sometimes reduce any unforeseen challenges.</p><p>Our technical team consist with well educated background knowing each and everything about the devices and their handling and supporting our QC team to follow the strict quality testing process and innovating new ways and softwares to overcome any new defect or functionality issue occurred.</p><p>We specialize in supply Grade A Used mobile phones, Grade A Used mobiles, Grade AB Mobiles, phone parts and mobile phone accessories, such as mobile phone housing, mobile phone flex cable, mobile phone spare parts, mobile phone hands-free, mobile phone touch screen digitizer, mobile phone repair tools, mobile phone crystal case, mobile phone silicon case, mobile phone LCD display screens, mobile phone TPU case, unlock boxes, mobile phone repair tools, mobile phone leather case, mobile phone screen protector, mobile phone charger, mobile phone battery, memory card, and other qualitative mobile phone parts and accessories.</p><p>Our inventory is constantly growing drastically and if the part you are currently looking for isn’t listed then please contact us as it might be on its way or in the company and not listed yet on our website.</p><p>With over 3 years of experience we have gone into designing OEM products for some of our customers by knowing every aspect of the accessories, hand picking materials, we feel our product range caters for all types of companies. You can easily talk to us from 9:00 am to 6:00 pm from Monday to Friday, or send us an email anytime as you want, be it for information on products or availability of stock. <strong><em>You are always welcome</em></strong>.</p></div>
